10. the person who growszinnia is not to the left of the person who growsamaryllis##8
11. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person who growsrose##2
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
13. the malaysian is not to the right of the person who growsrose##8
